message: Dear Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product, which is tailored to meet your specific needs and valued at $12,000. Considering its high quality and the benefits it brings, I would like to extend an exclusive offer to you at a special price of $11,000. This is a unique opportunity to acquire a product that is worth more than what you're paying, ensuring you receive excellent value for your investment. Please let me know if you're interested in discussing this further.
